flowchart TD
    A[Start] --> B[Read start file argument or use gen0]
    B --> C{Start file exists?}
    C -- No --> D[Print missing-file error and exit]
    C -- Yes --> E[Load grid into array]
    E --> F[Clear screen and print title]
    F --> G[Display generation 0]
    G --> H[Set generation to 1]
    H --> I{Generation <= 10?}
    I -- No --> Q[Exit]
    I -- Yes --> J[Loop through each cell]
    J --> K[Count valid live neighbors]
    K --> L{Birth or survival rule met?}
    L -- Yes --> M[Mark cell alive]
    L -- No --> N[Mark cell dead]
    M --> O{More cells?}
    N --> O
    O -- Yes --> J
    O -- No --> P[Display new generation and live count]
    P --> R{Any cells alive?}
    R -- No --> S[Print no-cells-alive message and exit]
    R -- Yes --> T[Increment generation and sleep]
    T --> I
